#### **Pillar 2: Event Hosting & Customization**

**4.2.1 Event Creation Workflow (Monetized)**

**Step 0: Payment Gate (NEW FEATURE)**
- **Event Creation Charge**: ₹99-₹499 (variable by event type)
  - Standard sports (football, badminton, cricket, yoga): ₹99
  - Niche events (cacao ceremony, book club, art workshops): ₹199-₹299
  - Large tournaments/corporate events: ₹499
- **Purpose**: 
  - Ensure quality (hosts commit financially)
  - Reduce spam/fake events
  - Generate platform revenue
- **Payment Methods**: UPI, card, wallet
- **Refund Policy**: Full refund if event cancelled by host within 24 hours; otherwise no refund

**Step 1: Basic Event Info**
- **Event Type Selection** (Dropdown + Search):
  - Pre-set categories: Football, Badminton, Cricket, Yoga, Fitness, Running, Tennis, Basketball, Volleyball, etc.
  - Custom Event: Allow free-text input for bespoke events (Cacao Ceremony, Book Reading, Art Class, Pottery Workshop, etc.)
  - Each selection auto-suggests creation charge amount
- **Event Name & Description**:
  - Title (max 100 chars, e.g., "Sunday Morning Yoga at Indiranagar Park")
  - Detailed description (max 500 chars with markdown support)
  - Event cover image upload (landscape 16:9, optimized for mobile)

**Step 2: Skill-Based Customization**
- **Skill Level Definition** (for host's reference):
  - Host specifies event skill level: Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced, Mixed
  - This is **searchable + filterable** on discovery side
  - Host can add skill description (e.g., "Beginners welcome. Some yoga experience helpful.")
- **Player Requirements**:
  - Min/max players required
  - Age restrictions (optional)
  - Gender preferences (open, women-only, men-only, co-ed)
- **Host Role**: Instructor, Coach, Coordinator, Community Lead (affects badging)

**Step 3: Theme & Visual Customization (UNIQUE)**
- **Preset Themes** (Event Type-Based):
  - Yoga event → Calming palette (soft blues, earth tones), meditation icons, serene background
  - Football → Dynamic palette (vibrant blues/reds), soccer icons, energetic layout
  - Book Club → Literary palette (dark theme, serif fonts), book icons, minimalist design
  - Fitness → Bold palette (purples/oranges), strong typography, motivational copy
  - Cacao Ceremony → Warm palette (browns/golds), artistic imagery, centered layout
- **Custom Color Picker**:
  - Primary color (background or accent)
  - Secondary color (CTA buttons)
  - Text color (light/dark)
  - Preview real-time on sample event card
- **Font Selection**: 
  - Playful (Fredoka, Comic Sans–friendly)
  - Professional (Poppins, Inter)
  - Elegant (Playfair Display, serif)
  - Monospace (for tech/coding events)
- **Additional Customization**:
  - Custom event icon/emoji selection
  - Background pattern (solid, subtle gradient, pattern overlay)
  - Card style (flat, shadow, gradient border)

**Step 4: Scheduling & Venue**
- **Schedule**:
  - Single event date/time or recurring (weekly, bi-weekly, monthly)
  - Duration (30 min to 4 hours)
  - Timezone (auto-detect user timezone)
- **Venue**:
  - Search & select from registered venues (Turf Town–style integration)
  - OR manual address entry + google maps pin
  - Venue facilities display (parking, washrooms, equipment)
  - OR "Online Event" toggle (for virtual yoga, webinars, online games)

**Step 5: Pricing & Payment**
- **Event Entry Fee**:
  - Free event (community-building)
  - Paid event (₹50-₹5000 per participant)
  - Sliding scale (e.g., Early bird ₹200, Regular ₹300)
- **Pricing Model**:
  - Per participant (total = fee × attendees)
  - Per team (for cricket/football tournaments)
  - Flat fee (for workshops, ceremonies)
- **Commission Structure**:
  - Platform takes 10-15% of booking fees
  - Host receives 85-90%
  - Payment settlement: Weekly or monthly (configurable)
- **Promo Codes**: Host can create codes (e.g., "FRIEND50" for ₹50 discount)

**Step 6: Rules & Requirements**
- **Equipment**: Host specifies required gear (e.g., "Bring your own badminton racquet")
- **House Rules**: Text field for conduct guidelines (e.g., "No aggression, inclusive environment")
- **Cancellation Policy**: 
  - Free cancellation up to 24 hours before
  - 50% charge if cancelled 12-24 hours before
  - No refund if cancelled within 12 hours
- **Refund Policy for Participants**: Auto-refund if event cancelled by host

**Step 7: Review & Publish**
- **Preview**: Full event card rendering with custom theme
- **Checklist**: 
  - ✓ Event info complete
  - ✓ Theme customized
  - ✓ Pricing set
  - ✓ Venue confirmed
  - ✓ Rules defined
- **Publish Button**: Live immediately or schedule for future date
- **Event Link**: Shareable link (deeplink) with custom short URL (e.g., `eventhub.app/yoga-sunday`)

**4.2.2 Event Management Dashboard**
- **Quick Stats** (on host home):
  - Players joined / max capacity (progress bar)
  - Revenue generated this month (₹ display)
  - Average event rating (star display)
  - Upcoming events (next 7 days)
- **Attendee Management**:
  - List of confirmed participants (name, skill level, payment status)
  - Pending RSVPs (reminder button)
  - Waitlist (if capped)
  - No-show tracking (mark absent after event)
- **Event Editor**:
  - Edit event details (description, schedule, pricing—except if already booked)
  - Update theme/colors
  - Add/remove venue facilities
  - Extend capacity or close early
- **Communication Hub**:
  - Send broadcast message to all attendees (e.g., "Location change alert")
  - Check-in feature (host scans QR code or manual check-in)
  - Post-event follow-up template (thank you, feedback request, next event invite)
- **Cancellation & Refunds**:
  - Cancel event (auto-refunds all participants)
  - Refund individual participants (partial or full)
  - Track refund status

