### 4.2 MVP Feature Additions (From Brainstorming Session)

#### **Module 1: Discovery & Matching**
- **Skill-Based Matching Algorithm** (NEW MVP)
  - Build matching engine that recommends events 80%+ skill-aligned
  - Events show "Avg Skill Level" + distribution chart (e.g., "4 Beginners, 6 Intermediate, 2 Advanced")
  - Hosts can enforce "Intermediate Only" (turn away beginners at booking)
  - Hosts see suggested price increase if mixing skill levels
  - Increases repeat bookings and reduces bad experiences

- **Waitlist & Capacity Overflow** (NEW MVP)
  - When event is full, offer "Waitlist" option showing position
  - If someone cancels, next person gets 1-hour priority to book
  - If 10+ people on waitlist, dashboard suggests host add second session
  - Host creates overflow session → platform gives 50 EventCoins credit
  - Captures lost demand and encourages hosts to scale successful events

#### **Module 2: Event Creation & Hosting**
- **Host Certification Path** (NEW MVP)
  - Platform offers optional certification badges by event type
  - Hosts upload credentials (teaching certificates, qualifications)
  - Community can verify (e.g., "Yoga Alliance Certified" ✓)
  - Certified hosts get higher visibility in feed (separate filter available)
  - Opens monetization: Certification verification fee (₹199-₹499)
  - Addresses trust gap with new users and differentiates premium events

#### **Module 3: Social & Community**
- **Location-Based Social Graph** (NEW MVP)
  - Show friends attending same event (real-time notifications)
  - "Raj just joined! You know him" notifications
  - Post-event: Auto-create group chat for mutual friends who attended
  - Leaderboard: "Most Connected" users (attended events with 10+ different friends)
  - Badges like "Social Butterfly" for network engagement
  - Creates FOMO + network effect for organic virality

#### **Module 4: Payments & Revenue**
- **Group Booking with Split Payments** (NEW MVP)
  - "Create group" → invite friends → each pays their share via app
  - Friends get reminder notification to pay
  - Booking confirmed only when all payments collected
  - Organizer gets deposit protection (booking locked even if someone flakes)
  - Post-event: Shared expense tracker ("Rahul owes you ₹250")
  - Reduces booking abandonment and increases average party size

- **Recurring Event Bundles** (NEW MVP)
  - "Subscribe to Priya's Sunday Yoga - ₹1800/month for 4 sessions" (15% savings)
  - Auto-booking each occurrence (can cancel individual session)
  - Hosts earn ₹1800 upfront (cash flow boost)
  - Platform takes 10% of bundle
  - Users get ₹50 EventCoins bonus for subscribing
  - Predictable revenue for hosts + reduces participant churn

#### **Module 5: B2B & Enterprise**
- **Corporate/B2B Event Module** (NEW MVP)
  - Separate "EventHub for Teams" tier for corporate HR
  - Volume discounts: 50+ people = 20% off booking fees
  - Admin portal: manage team roster, attendance tracking, expense allocation
  - Reporting: engagement scores, employee participation metrics
  - Annual contracts: ₹5-50 lakhs/year (bulk booking commitment)
  - Dedicated Account Manager for enterprise clients
  - Creates defensible moat with higher LTV than consumer

